Retrieve a character vector of expected config keys

Source: R/config-template.R
get_cfg_template_keys.Rd

Retrieve a character vector of expected config keys

Usage

get_cfg_template_keys()

Value

A character vector of expected config keys.

Details

The returned keys should be the same as those returned by get_cfg_keys(cfg = generate_cfg_template()).

Examples
